query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ado.net',
'apple-push-notifications',
'artificial-intelligence',
'build.gradle',
'export-to-csv',
'handlebars.js',
'href',
'navbar',
'navigation-drawer',
'prepared-statement',
'query-performance',
'uiimage',
'windows-services',
'word-vba');
